<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ rwḥ ạllh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạrwḥ ạllh ạmlk ʿlyạ wạmlạny yạrwḥ ạllh sd ʿly fkry wwjdạny

[V2]
 yạrwḥ ạllh ạlhb qlby wkyạny yạrwḥ ạllh ạmsḥ ạydy wlsạny

[V3]
 2- yạrwḥ ạllh qds nẓry wạwqạty yạrwḥ ạllh ḥdd ạnt ʿlạqạty

[V4]
 yạrwḥ ạllh ạḥyy ʿẓạmy wṣlạty yạrwḥ ạllh ạẓhr tẖmrk fy ḥyạty

[V5]
 3- yạrwḥ ạllh jdd zhny wạḥlạmy yạrwḥ ạllh qdny fy kl ạyạmy

[V6]
 yạrwḥ ạllh ạʿn ḍʿf ạymạny yạrwḥ ạllh ạʿln ḥqk fy klạmy

[V7]
 4- yạrwḥ ạllh zd ḥby lly fdạny yạrwḥ ạllh jhzny lmjyỷẗ ạltạny

[V8]
 yạrwḥ ạllh frḥny fy kl ạḥzạny yạrwḥ ạllh mstnyk tyjy bạgẖạny

[V9]
 5- yạrwḥ ạllh kẖlyny ạṣbr fy ḍyqạty yạrwḥ ạllh ạsẖhd ʿnk fy ḥyạty

[V10]
 yạrwḥ ạllh kẖlyny tẖạbt fy ạymạny yạrwḥ ạllh nwr ạnt kl ạyạmy

[V11]
 6- yạrwḥ ạllh qwyny bṣlyb ạlfạdy yạrwḥ ạllh ạḥmyny mn ʿạlm fạny

[V12]
 yạrwḥ ạllh yạ ḍạmn dạymạaⁿ slạmy yạ rwḥ ạllh tʿạly ạskn fy dyạry</lyrics>
<author>ạlqs fkẖry yʿqwb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10341</hymn_number>
</song>